procedure report;

{
Effects
By: Nashi
Description: Will return the effect to be typed by the script
}
function Effects: String;
var
Effectss: TStringArray;
begin
Effectss := [‘slide:’, ‘shake:’, ‘scroll:’, ‘wave:’, ‘wave2:’, ‘’];
if (effect <> ‘’) and (effect <> ‘random’) then
Result := effect
else
Result := Effectss[Random(GetArrayLength(Effectss))];
end;
{
Colors
By: Nashi
Description: Will give the colour to be typed by script

function Colors: String;

Colours: TStringArray;

Result := colour
else
Result := Colours[Random(GetArrayLength(colours))];
end;

{*******************************************************************************
anti randoms
By: SRL
Description: stops anti randoms from stuffing the script
*******************************************************************************}
procedure AntiRandom;
begin
FindTalk;
FindNormalRandoms;
FindLamp(‘defence’);
if FindFight then
begin
RunAwayDirection(‘S’);
Wait(10000+random(2000));
RunBack;
end;
end;

{*******************************************************************************
typer
By: sonny bill 9
Description: types the message(most important part of script)
*******************************************************************************}

procedure typer;
begin
if Random(2) = 0 then
TypeSend(humanText(Colors + Effects + yourmessage, Chance))
else
TypeSend(Colors + Effects + yourmessage);
wait(waittime);
sent:= sent + 1
end;

{*******************************************************************************
main loop
By: sonny bill 9
Description: runs the script
*******************************************************************************}
begin
setupsrl;
cleardebug;
maininitform;
activateclient;
setScreenName(yournick);
repeat
typer;
report;
until(isfkeydown(10))
